{"tid":110947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國寶物鑑定會　民眾以為是古董卻9成是假貨","createTime":"2017-02-07T05:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T15:39:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"734aa337a1ee182b213e97c72e7fa782605924b7","tid":110947,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php8aoNAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php8aoNAy.jpg&h=68305c7a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國武侯祠博物館每年都會舉辦專家鑑寶活動，民眾會將家中的古物帶到帶到現場鑑定，但4日舉辦的鑑寶活動中，現場有9成都是假貨。（圖截自網路）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國四川省成都武侯祠博物館每年都會舉辦專家鑑寶活動，許多民眾會將家中的古物帶到帶到現場鑑定，有外媒報導指出，武侯祠博物館於4日舉辦的鑑寶活動中，現場出現不少看似古老的瓷器、玉器、錢幣，但鑑定結果顯示，幾乎有9成都是假貨。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，錢幣專家袁愈高表示，一名胡姓男子帶來30枚清代的銀元，堅稱銀元是慈禧太后70大壽時鑄造，但據歷史記載，慈禧太后只有在60大壽時鑄造過銀幣，現在這種銀幣價值超過人民幣百萬元（約台幣450萬元），胡姓男子的「銀元」根本不含銀，其實只是一枚8元人民幣（約台幣36元）的假幣。<br />\n<br />\n另外，還有號稱有5000年歷史的馬家窯陶器，但從陶罐的泥灰與敲擊聲來判斷，其實就只是現代仿品而已，從鑑定會現場觀察，約有9成的古物被專家認定是贗品。就有古物專家建議，不具備專業知識就不要買舊貨收藏，且收藏一定要用閒錢，如此即便買到假貨也不會影響生活。"},{"pid":"70c78e7ae4ce881e1252781b511850ad35a45d12","tid":110947,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"最後央視揭發<br />\n<br />\n古物專家也是假的"},{"pid":"cbf56d29dcb84e4c8c713725e97f470409856cd4","tid":110947,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">還有號稱有5000年歷史的馬家窯陶器</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ad3619e31dd7fca01a55115615bccf460d38c7","tid":110947,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">還有號稱有5000年歷史的馬家窯陶器</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁撚過死海古卷呀"},{"pid":"10982dbf7fd7a41fa31d22bce87b23a0b79b5777","tid":110947,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後央視揭發<br />\n<br />\n古物專家也是假的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同啲人講話係假貨, 再低價買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04da24e7597a326317418cfca79607f9ebc5a73e","tid":110947,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後央視揭發<br />\n<br />\n古物專家也是假的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同啲人講話係假貨, 再低價買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cebb0c4dfcaa2c02059d194cd8e4b5a58ea93f","tid":110947,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後央視揭發<br />\n<br />\n古物專家也是假的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同啲人講話係假貨, 再低價買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點知真係假嘅"},{"pid":"bf6d3b0b60cfd2b437c599ac4d7b7452ad5c9028","tid":110947,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uc7mfeir\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuc7mfeir&h=a5b6c158&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83450cc8be093f60699acf7dcb757bd41a63dbba","tid":110947,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後央視揭發<br />\n<br />\n古物專家也是假的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同啲人講話係假貨, 再低價買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21745db8364405935ff37417a72b177046d886a","tid":110947,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0